RACE.RACE_TEXT: ARAPAHOE PARK RACE 4 5 1/2F Dirt CR: 56. Maiden Special Weight Purse 10700. FOR COLORADO BRED MAIDENS, FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 120 lbs.; Older, 124 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: MS BUMBLEBEE was roused to the front to a pressured lead, then bumped inside rival going into the turn, kept on to draw clear on the turn then was headed at the top of the stretch and dueled to the wire, won the nod. CHASING DIVINITY had good early speed, prompted the pace but was bumped going into the turn by outside rival, made a rebid at the top of the stretch and dueled to the wire and lost the nod. TUDIE LU was off slow, hustled to be off the pace around the turn and chased the top two to the wire. SHADOWINTHECLOUDS trailed the field and was outrun. A STEWARDS INQUIRY WAS POSTED INTO THE RUNNING AT THE THREE AND A HALF MARKER, ALSO A JOCKEY OBJECTION WAS POSTED, THE JOCKEY OF CHASING DIVINITY CLAIMED FOUL AGAINST THE JOCKEY OF MS BUMBLEBEE FOR INTERFERENCE AT THE THREE AND A HALF MARKER, AFTER A REVIEW THE CLAIM OF FOUL WAS ALLOWED AND MS BUMBLEBEE WAS DISQUALIFED FROM FIRST TO SECOND FOR INTERFERENCE ENTERING THE TURN.

ENTRY.COMMENT: off slow, hustled along, chased leaders
